CS251: Assignment 2 clarifications
Inbox
x

Deepak Chhikara <deepakchhikara66@gmail.com>
11:02 AM (2 hours ago)
to baman, kmrabhi, ashokk, buvivek, nishanth, kumawath, prahkg, nishants, rajatch, ajayraj, akshatb, luckys, amanan, amitkmr, amitkm, anpandey, ankitap, anurag, rahume, aradhana, sapgan, abashu, avikalpg, vicki, mmahore 
Hi:

Part1:
There have been many queries regarding mmv command.So I want to clarify
that you have to write your own command which works same as mmv like move
single file to single destination, single file to multiple destination,
multiple file to multiple destination etc. You can't use unix inbuilt mmv
command although you can use mv, cp commands.

Part2:
I'm attaching one sample input file and one sample output file for your
testing purpose. PFA.
Also I have added one more task in it of displaying ipaddress only, its an
extremely easy task and you will learn three useful commands also.

Regarding submission :

You all have to submit 3 files: Read me, script for part1, script for
part2 before 19 AUG' 2013 12:00PM. At the time of the demo the file will
be downloaded from moodle.

For further queries mail me or post in the FB group.

Thanks & Regards,
Deepak Chhikara
chhikara@iitk.ac.in
